Please ignore my last comment I have cracked it!  This is how for anyone who needs help:
To activate:
Download this .torrent and start the keygen.
Navigate to the "Crack" folder, and start the keygen.
When it asks to enter a serial, generate a serial from the keygen.
Let it continue installing.
When finished, look for the "Activate This Product" screen and Choose "Other", then "Activate By Phone".
Enter the code it gives you in the installer into the keygen, and click "Activation Code" in the keygen.
Copy that into the installer, and you're done! Happy Photoshoppin'!
